The code has all three parts ie minmax, aplha beta pruning and depth limited search.
The code is segmented into functions.
The functions are:
maxconnect4() 		: the function as asked for in the code that decides which mode
minmax()      		: the functoin that calculates the minmax value
scoreOfGame   		: prints the score of the board for each player
printBoard		: print the current state of the board.
checkBoardPlayable	: check if the board has playable moves
